Titolo: Slime Rancher

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Slime Rancher is a first-person life simulation adventure video game developed and published by American indie studio Monomi Park. The game was released as an early access title in January 2016, with an official release on Windows, macOS, Linux and Xbox One on August 1, 2017. A PlayStation 4 version was released on August 21, 2018, and a Nintendo Switch version was released on August 11, 2021. A DLC known as the secret style pack was released on June 18, 2019. A sequel, Slime Rancher 2, is set to be released in 2022 for Windows and Xbox Series X/S.

Genere: Life simulation 

Valutazione: 76
